      "content": "---\ntitle: 使用 DOCKER 容器安装 ODOO\nupdated: 2019-04-29 19:31:25Z\ncreated: 2019-04-29 19:31:04Z\nauthor: tangyongfeng@gmail.com\n---\n\n\n<en-note><div STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);-en-paragraph:true;\">Docker是一个便捷运行应用的跨平台解决方案，可在 MacOS, Linux 和 Windows 上使用。与传统的虚拟机相比，容器技术使用更为简单、资源利用率更高。首先需要在操作系统中安装 Docker，可从</span><a HREF=\"https://www.docker.com/\" STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(24, 188, 156); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);-en-paragraph:true;\">Docker官网</a><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);-en-paragraph:true;\">上下载免费使用的Docker CE（社区版），最新安装方法可在 Docker官网上查看。\n</span></div><div STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);-en-paragraph:true;\">应该注意虚拟化要求在 BIOS配置中进行开启，并且 Windows 版本的 Docker CE 需要有 Hyper-V，它仅在 Windows 10 企业版或教育版才会带有(</span><a HREF=\"https://docs.docker.com/docker-for-windows/install/\" STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(24, 188, 156); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);-en-paragraph:true;\">Windows 系统要求</a><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);-en-paragraph:true;\">)，而 Mac系统需要为 OS X El Capitan 10.11或更新版本。对于其它的 Windows 和 MacOS 版本，应安装&nbsp;</span><a HREF=\"https://docs.docker.com/toolbox/overview/\" STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(24, 188, 156); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);-en-paragraph:true;\">Docker Toolbox</a><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);-en-paragraph:true;\">，Docker Toolbox打包了 VirtualBox 并提供了预设置的 shell，用于作为操作 Docker 容器的命令行环境。\n</span></div><div STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);-en-paragraph:true;\">在&nbsp;</span><a HREF=\"https://store.docker.com/images/odoo\" STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(24, 188, 156); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);-en-paragraph:true;\">Odoo 商店</a><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);-en-paragraph:true;\">中包含 Odoo 镜像，在那里找到对应版本，按照提示进行安装。要使用 Docker运行 Odoo，我们需要两个容器，一个运行 PostgreSQL 数据库，一个运行 Odoo 服务。\n</span></div><div STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);-en-paragraph:true;\">安装通过命令行窗口完成，安装 PostgreSQL 容器\n</span></div><div STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; padding: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; max-height: 350px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: normal; color: rgb(205, 168, 105); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; max-height: 350px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(35, 35, 35); white-space: pre; min-width: 100%;\">docker</span><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: normal; color: rgb(230, 225, 220); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; max-height: 350px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(35, 35, 35); white-space: pre; min-width: 100%;\"> run -d -e POSTGRES_USER=odoo -e POSTGRES_PASSWORD=odoo -e POSTGRES_DB=postgres --name db postgres:</span><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: normal; color: rgb(165, 194, 97); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; max-height: 350px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(35, 35, 35); white-space: pre; min-width: 100%;\">10</span></div><div STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);-en-paragraph:true;\">此时便会从互联网上下载最新的 PostgreSQL 镜像，并在后台开启一个容器来进行运行。\n</span></div><div STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: Lato, &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);-en-paragraph:true;\">接下来安装 Odoo 服务容器，并且连接刚刚启动的 PostgreSQL 容器，暴露8069端口：\n</span></div><div STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; padding: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; max-height: 350px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: normal; color: rgb(194, 98, 48); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; max-height: 350px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(35, 35, 35); white-space: pre; min-width: 100%;\">docker</span><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: normal; color: rgb(230, 225, 220); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; max-height: 350px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(35, 35, 35); white-space: pre; min-width: 100%;\"> </span><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: normal; color: rgb(194, 98, 48); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; max-height: 350px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(35, 35, 35); white-space: pre; min-width: 100%;\">run</span><span STYLE=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-all; overflow-wrap: normal; color: rgb(230, 225, 220); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; max-height: 350px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-tr